(23, 'SharePoint Migration and Integration', 'sharepoint-migration-and-integration', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Let\r\nyour Business Data always be your strength. Get your Legacy Systems geared up\r\nfor current technologies</span></b><b>.<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">It is a must that businesses keep pace with\r\ncurrent technology. Our team of SharePoint engineers at CDRM Solutions, Inc.\r\nwill redesign and reconfigure your business platform when migrating</span> your business data<span lang=\"EN-IN\">.\r\nThe data will be migrated and integrated to advanced systems. Your data systems\r\nwill be configured for delivering better business outcomes. We are committed to\r\nserve your business needs. Call us at</span> (604) 783-4003 <span lang=\"EN-IN\">or email us at info@cdrmsolutions.com</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\">What\r\ncan </span></b><b>we <span lang=\"EN-IN\">do with SharePoint Migration and Integration\r\nServices?<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">The SharePoint Migration Tool (SPMT)</span>is a<span lang=\"EN-IN\">powerful technology\r\nfor data or content migration. We aid in content migration from on-premises\r\nSharePoint sites to Microsoft 365. With SharePoint Assessment Tool we assess\r\nand identify data migration issues and address them for secure total migration\r\nwithout any data loss.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\">We cover data migration under following\r\nroutes</span></b><b>:<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:21.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ã¼<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &q