(27, 'Data Management', 'data-management', '<p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Data Management is integral to business excellence. We at CDRM Solutions Inc., are vastly experienced in providing a host of Data Management Solutions. In fact, Data Management as a Service (DMaaS) is one of the main services we provide. The services we provide toward Data Management as a Service includes:</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data Streamlining:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">We process and transform raw data into the appropriate format using ETLs (Extract, Transform and Load) technique and tools. This makes data apt for analysis, refining the improved data, making further amendments and organizing it into manageable data sets.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data modeling:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Data models will be built around your business needs.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data architecture:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">We will define data architecture leading to a formalized and standard way of creating and managing data flow.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data pipelines:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Our develop and design appropriate data pipelines for swift and automated data transfer to data warehouses.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data catalogs:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Data Catalogs developed for managing metadata. This is done to map changes, locations, and quality whenever the data is being handled.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data warehouses:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Please check our service regarding Data Warehousing here.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data governance:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">We will define processes and policies standardizing your data management process ensuring high data security and integrity.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data security:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Protocols for layers of rights and privileges to data access will be defined for data security.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Our Data Management Solution provides security and scalability to your data, enabling you to make best use of your business intelligence. Feel free to email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a> or call us at&nbsp;us at 604 783 4003 for any of your data management needs.</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"></font><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Data Management is integral to business excellence. We at CDRM Solutions Inc., are vastly experienced in providing a host of Data Management Solutions.</span><br></p>', 'data-management56746.jpg', '8', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-13 12:03:29.432206', '2021-11-10 05:03:42.000000'),
(28, 'Artificial Intelligence', 'artificial-intelligence', '<p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We at CDRM Solution will leverage the power of AI in delivering the following services and more:</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Smart Workflows:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">We leverage AI to redefine your workflows.&nbsp; AI driven workflows are much smarter as they are derived and driven by the business intelligence extracted from your data. Therefore, our Smart AI driven workflows help in enhancement of your team capabilities and performance leading to improved business outcomes.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>AI driven Custom Care solutions:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">AI driven custom care assistants such as chat bots using real-time data engage with customers virtually with 24x7 presence thereby enhancing customer experience with your business.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Business Intelligence Analytics:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Our AI experts by deploying AI Solutions driven by machine learning and deep learning, help you extract from your own data; new trends and customer needs providing new insights to engage with customers, adding new value to products and services and making better business decisions.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>AI Enterprise Solutions:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Enterprise AI Solutions transform your data management, supply chains, business process, human resource management and all other business functions in a revolutionary way. To know more, call us at 604 783 4003 or simply email us at </span><a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a></p><div><br></div>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We at CDRM Solution will leverage the power of AI in delivering the following services and more:</span><br></p>', 'ai53916.jpg', '8', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-13 12:04:12.110405', '2021-11-10 05:05:01.000000'),
(29, 'Business Intelligence', 'business-intelligence', '<p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We at CDRM Solutions by virtue of our expertise in Data Management, Artificial Intelligence, Data Analytics are perfectly placed to provide smarter Business Intelligence (BI) Services.</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Our Business Intelligence solutions include:</b></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data mining:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Leveraging our expertise in Machine Learning and AI, our team provides Data Mining services for extracting business intelligence from large databases and large datasets.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Metrics and benchmarking:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">We help uncover outcome-metrics by designing a system that compares present data and historical data on defined metrics. You can set new benchmarks to improve your performances.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data visualization:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">We design a system that transforms data analysis reports quickly into easily comprehensible charts, graphs and histograms.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Data preparation:&nbsp;</b></span></font><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px; color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Compilation collation of data from multiple sources arranged for quick data analysis.&nbsp;</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">In fact, there is so much more we can do. Our team of seasoned professionals in the field of Artificial Intelligence, Business Intelligence, Database Experts, Statisticians, Mathematicians and many other professionals will work for you. Call us at 604 783 4003 or email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a> and we will love to show you how we can make the difference.</span></font></p>', '<p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We at CDRM Solutions by virtue of our expertise in Data Management, Artificial Intelligence, Data Analytics are perfectly placed to provide smarter Business Intelligence (BI) Services.</span></font><br></p>', 'bi35556.jpg', '8', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-13 12:05:00.319205', '2021-11-10 05:05:51.000000'),
(30, 'Integrated Existing System to Infrastructure', 'integrated-existing-system-to-infrastructure', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">By using Integrated Existing system to Infrastructure tools the clients can manage a large number of applications and tools by managing a single system. This can help in easier operation as well as making it a more efficient and less time-consuming process.</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">By using Integrated Existing system to Infrastructure tools the clients can manage a large number of applications</span><br></p>', 'integrated-existing-system78912.jpg', '9', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-13 12:07:27.847698', '2021-10-22 12:14:36.000000'),
(31, 'Custom Integration Solutions', 'custom-integration-solutions', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">These integrations of several tools into one can be made specific and discrete as per the company. For this, the clients seek the expertise of the CDRM Solutions Inc team. We provide the most suitable and unique system for each company to resolve such issues.</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">These integrations of several tools into one can be made specific and discrete as per the company</span><br></p>', 'integration-solution31152.jpg', '9', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-13 12:08:24.040538', '2021-10-22 12:14:40.000000'),
(32, 'Simplifying Complex Data for Businesses', 'simplifying-complex-data-for-businesses', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Businesses can have a large amount of complex data which needs to be simplified in order to access by all the employees with ease. We offer our dedicated services to the clients to make such service which resolves the purpose of Simplifying Complex Data for business.</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Businesses can have a large amount of complex data which needs to be simplified in order to access by all the employees</span><br></p>', 'Simplifying67882.jpg', '9', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-13 12:09:35.540841', '2021-10-22 12:14:44.000000'),
(33, 'Process Management and Optimization / Auditing', 'process-management-and-optimization-auditing', '<p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Documents and information are created every day in a business enterprise. Information and Document Management systems ensure that the business information is systematically stored and easy to retrieve. A sound document management process and system also ensure business information is safe and free from any security breaches.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>What will we do to optimize Information Document Process Management and Optimization?</b></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We at CDRM Solution will help you optimize document and information asset management by building logical, secure processes for document management. We do so by auditing the existing processes and improving them by placing the business information security, ease of storage and quick retrieval at the center of the document and information management process.</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Our focus areas while devising and optimizing an Information Document Process are:</b></span></font></p><ul><li><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Audit of existing business information creation, and storage process</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Optimize Document Capturing</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Document Storage and Archiving</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Analyzing and Optimizing Business Document Workflows</span></font></li><li><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Integrations</span></font></li></ul><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b></b></span><br></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Process Audit</b></span><br></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">The first process is audit of existing workflows and understanding creation and storage of information. Based on the audit, we highlight key areas that require improvement and enhancements.</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Document Workflow Management</b></span><br></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Document workflow management is a consciously adopted system designed for creation, modification, storage, and retrieval of business documents. At CDRM Solutions, we will create business workflows that let you create and store business data in a defined structured way ensuring quick retrieval of the desired information across all teams.</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Integration</b></span><br></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We will help you integrate different teams to create, store business data with pre-defined tags. The system we design ensures that data is not open 