(34, 'Electronic Document Management System Support', 'electronic-document-management-system-support', '<p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">Electronic Document Management System is a new revolutionary way of adding energy and swiftness within the business operation by seamlessly connecting different business processes together with information.&nbsp; When the speed at which business decisions are taken, EDM services become the excellence differentiators. We at CDRM Solutions are committed to help you make the digital leap.</span></font><br></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>How will we revolutionize your Electronic Document Management System?</b></span></font><br></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><b>Database driven structured database naming and storage</b></span></font></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 104, 128); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We at CDRM Solutions Inc. will design a system by which the file and documents will be indexed and stored in a structured way. We also define a file naming system and structure so that file and folder are quickly traceable and retrievable.</span></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Browser based Document Management System</span></span><br></font></p><p><font color=\"#5b6880\" face=\"Rubik, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">We will provide for a browser-based Document Management System web client for routine business work. Each workstation accesses the Document Management Software through a browser of your choice. We can upload the Document Management Software up on the cloud, your user can access i