(54, 'Web Deployment', 'web_deployment', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Website is collection of many components\r\nsuch as payment gateway, product catalogue management, Shopping cart, customer\r\nsupport and many other components. These components are nowadays available as\r\nplugins which need to integrate and implement. We at CDRM Solutions Inc help deploy a website\r\nwith different plugins and components which are seamlessly integrated to\r\nfunction as well-oiled machine.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Â As\r\nmentioned, we offer a wide ranging services, please feel free to call us at +1\r\n(604) 783-4003 or email us <u><span style=\"color:blue\"><a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\"><span style=\"color:blue\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</span></a></span></u>\r\nat to see what we can do for your projects.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Website is collection of many components such as payment gateway, product catalogue management, Shopping cart, customer supportÂ <br></p>', 'e-comerance89238.jpg', '19', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-13 13:09:38.601049', '2021-10-22 12:17:01.000000'),
(55, 'Search Engine Optimization', 'search-engine-optimization', '<p>Search Engine Optimization is a technique to optimize the website and the respective web pages for the search engines. Search Engine Optimization makes the content and design of the website search engine friendly. We at CDRM Solutions IncÂ  will optimize the web pages, the content on the entire website such that the search engines accept and promote the webpages as relevant and best content. Contact us by phone at +1 (604) 783-4003 or simply send us an email at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a> and we will organize a meeting to discuss your needs and challenges to chalking out a winning SEO strategy.<br></p>', '<p>Search Engine Optimization is a technique to optimize the website and the respective web pages for the search engines. Search Engine Optimization makes the content and design of the website search engine friendly.Â <br></p>', 'keyword-research26069.jpg', '20', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-19 10:27:46.164614', '2021-11-18 07:13:10.000000'),
(56, 'Social Media Management', 'social-media-management', '<p>Social Media has become the lifeline for both individual and business enterprises. CDRM Solutions Inc devises most relevant and adaptive Social Media strategies to leveraging the potency of the powerful social media platforms.We help clients harness the goodness of Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn and other social media platforms to engage with their customers on a day-to-today basis and stay in tune with the changing times.</p>', '<p>Social Media has become the lifeline for both individual and business enterprises. CDRM Solutions Inc devises most relevant and adaptive Social Media strategies to leveraging the potency of the powerful social media platforms.Â <br></p>', 'digital-marketing81844.jpg', '20', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-19 10:36:53.940458', '2021-11-19 08:30:41.000000'),
(57, 'Digital Marketing Analytics', 'digital-marketing -analytics', '<p>Search Engine Optimization and Social Media Management require analysis. We at CDRM Solutions Inc constantly fine tune SEO and SMM strategies based on interpretation of data analytics of key performance indicators. We push and bolster strategies that provide greater returns and chop n change the strategies that are providing less than optimal results to provide greater thrust to digital marketing initiatives. Call us at +1 (604) 783-4003 or email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmsolutions.com </a>Â for analysis of your current digital presence.<br></p>', '<p>Search Engine Optimization and Social Media Management require analysis. We at CDRM Solutions Inc constantly fine tune SEO and SMM strategies based on interpretation of data analytics of key performance indicators.<br></p>', 'data-management5674639861.jpg', '20', '1', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', '2021-10-19 10:38:16.635490', '2021-10-22 12:17:14.000000'),
(58, 'Custom App Development Services', 'custom-app-development-services', '<p>We have a purpose driven Custom App Development Teamof business and technology professionals. At the outset the team takes a holistic view of the unique business and technology challenges faced by your business. Then we partner with you in the design and development of a mobile app. The mobile app we at CDRM develop will be developed afresh. It will not be an adoption or modification of a ready-made template available in the market. Our teaminvolves you in every process of design and development ensures that the app is addressing your specific business needs completely. Custom App so developed integrates even third-party tools seamlessly and of course will run on both Android and iOS platforms.Â </p><p><br></p>', '<p>We have a purpose driven Custom App Development Teamof business and technology professionals. At the outset the team takes a holistic view of the unique business and technology challenges faced by your business.Â </p><p><br></p>', 'H0f3836ae8e96424c839212ad0f8e44e1K73142.png', '15', '1', '', '', '2021-11-08 05:26:50.151721', '2021-11-08 05:35:53.000000'),
(59, 'Android Mobile App Development', 'android-app-development', '<p>Our Android Mobile App development team is competent at leveraging Android Bumblebee, Android Studio Chipmunk Canary and other Android platforms available. The team is equally adept at deploying Jetpack, and Kotlin. Both technical and business teams are abreast with most recent Android releases, latest developments at Google Play helping you in more ways in empowering your business.</p>', '<p>Our Android Mobile App development team is competent at leveraging Android Bumblebee, Android Studio Chipmunk Canary and other Android platforms available. The team is equally adept at deploying Jetpack, and Kotlin.Â <br></p>', 'android-application-services-189930548501.jpeg', '15', '1', '', '', '2021-11-08 05:39:31.305587', '2021-11-08 05:44:28.000000'),
(60, 'iOS Mobile App Development', 'ios-app-development', '<p>A customer and a business committed to iOS has a very different profile. Knowing fully well that managing Apple hardware and software requires a different set of skills and understanding, we at CDRM have a separate team for iOS app development. Our technical team includes professionals who have a thorough understanding of all aspects of XCode â€“ the integrated development environment for macOS. The team includes programmers skilled in Objective C and Swift languages. In addition to programmers, our team have specialists capable of tapping into most of the maacOS APIs and libraries. We make sure no stone is left unturned in developing the optimal iOS Mobile app for your businesses.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">For iOS mobile App development, you can\r\nreach us at +1 (604) 783-4003. You can email us too at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a></span></p>', '<p>A customer and a business committed to iOS has a very different profile. Knowing fully well that managing Apple hardware and software requires a different set of skills and understanding, we at CDRM have a separate team for iOS app development.Â <br></p>', 'mobile-application-development-500x50099776.jpg', '15', '1', '', '', '2021-11-08 05:49:01.980083', '2021-11-08 06:04:34.000000');
