(61, 'Cross-Platform Mobile Apps', 'cross-platform-apps', '<p>For businesses having customers using both Android and iOS platform based mobile devices, cross-platform apps work best for them. Cross-platform apps work like native apps on both iOS and Android platforms.Â </p><p>For cross-platform apps too, we do have a dedicated resource team experienced in Ionic, ReactNative, Xamarin, Flutter and many other technologies. The skill set of the app development team extends to managing a wide range of compilers, set of libraries, tools, and different frameworks.Â </p><p>App development is a structured process. Do call us at +1 (604) 783-4003 we will listen to your requirements and quickly give you an assessment on the minimum viable product (MVP) and a financial quotation as well. You can request a quote by emailing us at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a> and we will get back to you immediately.</p>', '<p>For businesses having customers using both Android and iOS platform based mobile devices, cross-platform apps work best for them. Cross-platform apps work like native apps on both iOS and Android platforms.Â <br></p>', 'cross-platform-development25050.png', '15', '1', '', '', '2021-11-08 05:56:18.319134', '2021-11-08 06:00:54.000000');

