(4, 'Website Design & Development', 'website-design-development', 'CDRM Solutions Inc is one of the top-notch service providers in Website Designing and Development. At CDRM Solutions Inc we cover almost all aspects of website design and development. Our services cover simpler WordPress websites to highly customized websites including E-commerce catalogue websites.Ensuring widest range of services under a single roof for online stores and businesses, we have set up specialized teams having expertise in critical aspects of website designing and development, such as UX and UI, Payment Gateway integration, E-commerce catalogues, chatbots and most importantly Mobile App Development.<br><br>In addition to core website design and development services, we also provide our clients services for advertising and marketing of the website under Digital Marketing. Under Digital Marketing we cover services namely Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Social Media Marketing (SMM), Content Marketing and many other related services. Website designing and development can be challenging, let us partner with you in sharing and expertise with you in helping you achieve the milestone of success you wish to achieve. We would love to go the distance with you. Give us a call at +1 604 803 4003, leave you number or email your contact information and we will initiate the discussion and build a fruitful future.&nbsp;<br>', '<ul><li>Mobile App Development</li><li>Ecommerce & Catalogues and Website</li><li>Internet Digital Marketing</li><li>Website Design & Development</li><li>Search Engine Optimization</li></ul>', 'websitedesign14674360144.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc is a Vancouver web design and development company focused on building high-quality websites for small businesses. For more information visit our website.', 'web design company Vancouver, website development company', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:30:41.100400', '2021-11-13 05:28:30.000000'),
(5, 'Microsoft & Cloud Solutions Consulting', 'microsoft-consulting', '<p>CDRM Solution is adept at providing most advanced Cloud Integration services involving cloud-to-cloud, cloud-toon-premises integration and a combination of the two. Our team at CDRM Solutions have in-depth knowledge and proven experience of Cloud integration and cloud data integration tools.</p><p><b>Our agile and scalable Cloud Integration Solutions entails:Â </b></p><ul><li>Data FlexibilityÂ </li><li>Data ScalabilityÂ </li><li>Data IntegrationÂ </li></ul><p>Our Cloud Integration solutions is capable of handling diverse business components which include both data and applications.</p><p><b>Our Services can be classified in to two main types:</b></p><ul><li>Data integration: The integration is focused on data-related synchronization through cloud-based solutions.</li><li>Application integration: Under Application Integration, our team strives to connect different applications for seamless integration and functionality.Â </li></ul><p>To learn how our cloud integration solutions can make a big difference to your business excellence drive. Call us at 604 783 4003 or email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a></p>', '<ul><li>Cloud Development and Integration</li><li>Cloud Architecture and Migration<br></li></ul>', 'microsoft11105689482.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:32:39.882454', '2021-11-12 05:39:03.000000'),
(6, 'Power Platform Consulting', 'power-platform-consulting', '<p>CDRM Solutions Inc. is one of the leading service providers in Power BI Development. Our highly experienced team of Certified Power BI developers design BI environments delivering optimal value. Our teamâ€™s expertise in structured Azure, C#, SQL, data modelling and management, is at par with the best in the industry. We have established intelligence solutions that efficiently utilize data.<br></p>', '<ul><li>Power BI Development</li><li>Power BI Implementation</li><li>Creating and customizing Macros in Excel<br></li></ul>', 'power-platform4169756950.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:33:47.715240', '2021-11-11 04:48:29.000000'),
(7, 'Sharepoint Consulting', 'sharepoint-consulting', '<p>CDRM Solutions Inc offers services related to SharePoint such as Application Development, Integration, Customization, Migration, Ui, or Branding options to the client.<br></p>', '<ul><li>SharePoint Application Development</li><li>SharePoint Migration</li><li>SharePoint Integration</li><li>SharePoint Customization</li><li>SharePoint UI/Branding<br></li></ul>', 'sharepoint7812060380.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:35:19.505822', '2021-10-22 12:10:43.000000'),
(8, 'Data Analytics Consulting Services', 'data-analytics-consulting-services', '<p>The data analysis can be made easier and more efficient by using several tools. CDRM Solutions Inc offers services comprising tools such as Data Management, Machine Learning, and Advanced Analytics, and Data warehousing. They can help the client to analyze the data more effectively and at a faster pace.<br></p>', '<ul><li>Data Warehousing</li><li>Data Management</li><li>ML & Advanced Analytics</li><li>Business Intelligence<br></li></ul>', 'data-analytics9040659580.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:36:20.122908', '2021-10-22 12:10:47.000000'),
(9, 'System Integrations Consulting', 'system-integration-consulting', '<p>All the information technology management tools and systems are provided\r\n by CDRM Solutions Inc including Systems integrations and Microsoft solutions. It also\r\n provides services of Integrated Existing system to the sue of \r\nInfrastructure, Simplification of Complex data for business and \r\ncustomized system integrations.</p>', '<ul><li>Integrated Existing System to Infrastructure</li><li>Custom Integrations Solutions</li><li>Simplifying Complex Data for Businesses<br></li></ul>', 'microsoft11105688275.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:37:23.065855', '2021-10-22 12:10:54.000000'),
(10, 'Information & Document Management', 'information-document-management', 'Information and Document Management is a surefire way to achieve business excellence. At CDRM Solutions we understand the pivotal role Information and Document Management plays. Precisely why we have an array of solutions to help companies optimize their information and document management systems. Do contact us for your company needs and business objectives. We can be reached at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmcolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmcolutions.com</a>. You can also call us at 604 783 4003', '<ul><li>Process Management and Optimization / Auditing</li><li>Electronic document management system support<br></li></ul>', 'information9046840333.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:38:38.569868', '2021-11-03 04:55:03.000000'),
(11, 'Staffing & Training', 'staffing-training', '<p><b>Staffing</b></p><p>CDRM Solutions is a multi-solutions provider company. Our Staffing and Training service covers both technical and non-technical manpower for companies of all sizes.</p><p>Our staffing services team conducts AI driven intelligent profile and role matching processes for locating, selecting and recruiting personnel for business operations, technical departments, semi-technical divisions and other miscellaneous business functions in a company. The staffing process also includes a quality-conscious process of skill assessment drives for empirical proof of skill-levels. We also conduct strenuous background checks to find the best match.</p><p>Catering to diverse staffing needs, we head hunt for specialized positions and functions. In addition, we also find and recruit the best talent for all positions across a company.</p><p><b>Training</b></p><p>We at CDRM Solutions also cater to the training needs of our clients. We have a rich resource pool of trainers for both hard and soft skills. Our experienced trainers provide multi-layered skill training and process learning solutions to help enhance work performance.</p><p><b>We provide the following trainer services:</b></p><ul><li>Skill Gap Analysis</li><li>Technical Skill Training</li><li>Soft Skill Training</li><li>Six Sigma Training for certifications</li><li>Specialized training for customized technology solutions developed by CDRM</li><li>Pre-Training and Post Training Competency Evaluation</li><li>Training the Trainer</li></ul><div>Do contact us for your staffing and training needs. Call us at 604 783 4003 or email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a><br></div><div><br></div>', '<ul><li>Hiring and Scheduling Staff.</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'staffing4574120314.png', '1', '1', 'service', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', NULL, '2021-10-13 07:39:20.747463', '2021-11-12 05:44:10.000000'),
(13, 'Search Engine  Optimization', 'search-engine-optimization', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Search Engine Optimization is a\r\ncontinuously evolving technique of progressively building on the net value of\r\nwebsite traffic in terms of both quality and quality. SEO strives to work on\r\nboosting traffic through organic or unpaid website traffic to a specific\r\ntargeted web page and the website in whole. CDRM Solutions Inc in one of the\r\nleading providers of Search Engine Optimization services in Vancouver. CDRM Solutions Inc offer the following services for Search Engine Optimization campaigns.\r\nCall us or email us and say yes to effective Search Engine Optimization initiative.Â Â <o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Search Engine Optimization is a continuously evolving technique of progressively building on the net value of website trafficÂ <br></p>', '', '1', '0', 'resource', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'Vancouver ', '2021-10-13 08:22:37.070381', '2021-11-19 09:58:15.000000'),
(14, 'Local Seo Services ', 'local-seo-services', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Local SEO is services is key to market\r\ncapture and consolidation due to the fact that 9 out 10 consumers search for\r\nlocal businesses online. Localized SEO services results in effective lead\r\ngeneration in terms of call at help desks, email inquiries and instore visits.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">CDRM Solutions based in Surrey Vancouver\r\nprovides expert localized Search Engine Optimization Services.Â <o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Local SEO is services is key to market capture and consolidation due to the fact that 9 out 10 consumers search<br></p>', '', '1', '0', 'resource', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'Toronto', '2021-10-13 08:23:13.522050', '2021-11-19 10:36:42.000000'),
(15, 'Mobile App Development ', 'mobile-app-development', '<p>Mobile App is the gold standard of casting a wider net to touch, involve and engage with digitally influenced customers. We at CDRM Solutions Inc enjoy a distinction in offering forward-looking Mobile App Development services owing to our expertise in top Mobile App Framework including ReactNative, Flutter, Ionic, Felgo and knowledge of other frameworks too. We have a resource pool of software coders and programmers adept in C++, Java, Swift, HTML and other related languages to design and develop a successful mobile App. We develop native apps for both Android and iOS platform and Hybrid Mobile App or Cross-platform apps that work well on Android and iOS platforms, both.</p><p>In addition to the above, we are also experienced in the process of launching a mobile app in different online stores, their promotion and other business dynamics. Thereâ€™s so much more to Mobile Apps. So, if you have any queries related to mobile app development projects, feel free to connect with us at +1 604 803 4003. You can also email us atÂ <a href=\"mailto:info@cdrmsolutions.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">info@cdrmsolutions.com</a></p><p><b>CDRM Mobile App Development Process</b></p><ul><li>360<sup>o</sup> Research for Minimal Viable ProductÂ </li><li>Data Analysis and Planning</li><li>App UI & UX Design</li><li>Technical Development</li><li>Quality Analysis & Testing of MVP</li><li>Deployment & Support</li></ul><p><b>Key features that form the DNA of all our mobile app development process</b></p><ul><li>Scalability</li><li>Easy deployment</li><li>Security</li><li>Speed</li><li>UI and UX</li><li>Cost Effectiveness<br><br></li></ul>', '<p>Mobile App is the gold standard of casting a wider net to touch, involve and engage with digitally influenced customers. We at CDRM Solutions Inc enjoy a distinction in offering forward-looking Mobile App Development services owing to our expertise in