(20, 'Digital Marketing ', 'digital-marketing', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Digital Marketing is an initiative to promote a website through digital channels. We at CDRM Solutions Inc enjoy an advantageous position amongst digital marketing solutions providers by virtue of expertise, experience, and a dedicated team of professionals. We offer a wider range of digital marketing solutions to march ahead of the competitions.  We offer the below services.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<ul><li>Search Engine Optimization</li><li>Social Media Management</li><li>Digital Marketing Analytics</li></ul>', 'digital86936.png', '1', '0', 'resource', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'CDRM Solutions Inc', 'Toronto', '2021-10-19 10:24:10.253651', '2021-11-19 10:56:03.000000');

